    - target: {fileID: 1497534752906518004, guid: b3ad3ffe5d9ec684084b142d99857b31, type: 3}
      propertyPath: GameText
      value: "<b>1987 - Final Fantasy (Square, 1987).</b>\n\n-RPG\n-Player controls
        party of four \u201CLight Warriors\u201D\n-6 classes\n-Save the world by
        beating dark forces. \n\n-Player\u2019s characters displayed on the left,
        with enemies displayed on the right while in combat. \n-First of its kind
        to use this display. (Bregalad, 2017). \n\nThe development team also drew
        inspiration from <b>Wizardry </b>(Sir-Tech, 1981) (Parish, 2017)."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
