      propertyPath: GameText
      value: "<b>Rogue (A.I. Design, 1980)</b>\n\nRPG dungeon-crawler\n- Find a magical
        amulet at the bottom of a massive cave system, and go back up\n- Dont die.
        (Froholt, 2025). \n\n-Fight monsters in turn-based combat\n- Introduced Permadeath
        \n- Procedurally generated levels. \n\nInspired the Roguelike genre. (Froholt,
        2025)\n"
