--- !u!1001 &741870072
PrefabInstance:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  serializedVersion: 2
  m_Modification:
    serializedVersion: 3
    m_TransformParent: {fileID: 1481157370}
    m_Modifications:
    - target: {fileID: 1497534752906518004, guid: b3ad3ffe5d9ec684084b142d99857b31, type: 3}
      propertyPath: GameText
      value: "<b>1981 - Wizardry: Proving Grounds of the Mad Overlord. (Sir-Tech,
        1981)</b>\n\nAlso known as Wizardry\n-create party of up to 6 characters\n-
        5 races, 3 alignments, 4 basic classes, 4 advanced classes\n\n- Inspired
        by <b>Dungeons and Dragons 1st Edition</b>. (Roddison, 2024). \n- Explore,
        find treasure, level up by killing monsters, and then fight the last boss
        at the bottom of the level to get a powerful amulet.\n\nParty system and
        spell-slot system inspired the team behind <b>Final Fantasy</b> (Square,
        1987) (Parish, 2017)\n\nRandom enemy encounters also contributed to <b>Dragon
        Quest</b> (Enix, Spike Chunsoft, 1986). (Kalata, 2008)."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1497534752906518004, guid: b3ad3ffe5d9ec684084b142d99857b31, type: 3}
      propertyPath: FightTitle
      value: The wizard
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1497534752906518004, guid: b3ad3ffe5d9ec684084b142d99857b31, type: 3}
