--- !u!1001 &888678538
PrefabInstance:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  serializedVersion: 2
  m_Modification:
    serializedVersion: 3
    m_TransformParent: {fileID: 1481157370}
    m_Modifications:
    - target: {fileID: 1497534752906518004, guid: b3ad3ffe5d9ec684084b142d99857b31, type: 3}
      propertyPath: GameText
      value: "<b>1991 - Sid Meier\u2019s Civilisation.</b> (Microprose, 1991)\n\n-Turn-based
        strategy game \n-Player controls historical civilisation\n\nWin in 3 ways:\n-First
        to build a spaceship and complete a journey\n-Conquering the whole map\n-Most
        amount of points by the year 2100. (Sid Meier\u2019s Civilisation | Official
        Civilisation Site, n.d.)\n\nCore feature is the <b>4X gameplay loop: Explore,
        Expand, Exploit, Exterminate. </b>\n\n-Popularised the 4X genre, setting
        a <b>golden standard</b> for any games to come after it. (Singh, 2025)\n-Also
        created the addictive \u201COne more turn\u201D mechanic (Idcgames, 2024)"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1497534752906518004, guid: b3ad3ffe5d9ec684084b142d99857b31, type: 3}
      propertyPath: FightTitle
      value: Sid Meier
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1497534752906518004, guid: b3ad3ffe5d9ec684084b142d99857b31, type: 3}
      propertyPath: FightSprite
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 4d947c603f08aca4e94542e700e353fa, type: 3}
    - target: {fileID: 1497534752906518004, guid: b3ad3ffe5d9ec684084b142d99857b31, type: 3}
      propertyPath: ShadowSize.x
