    - target: {fileID: 1497534752906518004, guid: b3ad3ffe5d9ec684084b142d99857b31, type: 3}
      propertyPath: GameText
      value: "<b>1986 - Dragon Quest (Enix, Spike Chunsoft, 1986)</b>\n\n- Turn-based
        RPG\n- Knight whose mission is to save the princess of Alefgard from the
        evil Dragonlord and subsequently save the Kingdom of Alefgard.\n\nThe creator
        <b>Yuji Horii</b> combined first-person movements from <b>Wizardry</b> and
        top-down view from <b>Ultima</b> to create <b>Dragon Quest</b>. \n\nThe developers
        made a game which was easier to understand, letting busier users enjoy the
        game (DeMattia, 2020). \n\nCreated the <b>JRPG subgenre.</b> (Kalata, 2008)."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1497534752906518004, guid: b3ad3ffe5d9ec684084b142d99857b31, type: 3}
      propertyPath: FightTitle
      value: Pudgy Dragon
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
